{"lemma":"شَمَرِ","slug":"شَمَرِ","root":"ش.م.ر","root_slug":"ش-م-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-م-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":6,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n22966","n22967","n22971","n22972"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to tuck up, to raise"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to tuck up, to raise","examples":[{"text":"شَمَّرَ عَنْ سَاقَيْهِ","english":"to flee"},{"text":"شَمَّرَ عَنْ سَاعِدِ الجِدِّ","english":"to roll up one's sleeves"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَمَرَ (šamara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"light, agile, active, swift","tags":["rare"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fennel (Foeniculum gen.)","tags":["rare"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"dill (Anethum graveolens)","tags":["rare"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the Arabic tribe of Shammar","tags":["rare"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"ellipsis of إِمَارَةُ جَبَلِ شَمَّرَ (ʔimāratu jabali šammara, “Emirate of Jabal Shammar, a state derived from the tribe”)","tags":["abbreviation","alt-of","ellipsis","rare"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Aramaic, where attested forms include Jewish Babylonian Aramaic סִמְרָא, סִימְרָא (simrā), absolute state סְמַר (smar), Jewish Palestinian Aramaic שומרא (šummārā), Classical Syriac ܫܲܡܵܪܵܐ (šammārā) and ܫܘܼܡܵܪܵܐ (šummārā), all meaning fennel, deriving from Akkadian 𒌑𒄩 (šimru, simru, “fennel”), also found in Hebrew שֻׁמָּר (šummā́r, “fennel”) and שָׁמִיר (šāmī́r, “dill”), and likely Ugaritic 𐎘𐎎𐎗 (ṯmr, “likely fennel”). Related to Old Armenian շամրայ (šamray), շումրայ (šumray), a Semitic borrowing.\n\nFrom Old South Arabian 𐩦𐩣𐩧 (s²mr), occurring already BCE, in the earliest Middle Sabaean inscriptions."},"ipa":["/ʃam.mar/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22966","headword_ar":"شَمَرَ","root":"$mr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amorN","text_ar":"شَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph, in five places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n22967","headword_ar":"شمّر","root":"$mr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta$omiyrN","text_ar":"تَشْمِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tucked up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,) his garment, (Msb, K,) or his waist-wrapper, (S,) [or his sleeve,] or his skirts. (A.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$m~r Eano saAqihi","text_ar":"شمّر عَنْ سَاقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tucked up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"his garment, or waist-wrapper, or skirts,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from his shank"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) [And in like manner, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$m~r","text_ar":"تشمّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tucked up, his garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: for] one says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$m~r Eano saAEidayohi","text_ar":"تشمّر عَنْ سَاعِدَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He tucked up his sleeves from his fore arms"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$am~ara *ayolFA waA@d~araEa layolFA","text_ar":"شَمَّرَ ذَيْلًا وَا@دَّرَعَ لَيْلًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. [lit.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drew up, his"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skirt"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and clad himself with night as with a tunic"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amiro *ayolFA waA@d~ariEo layolFA","text_ar":"شَمِرْ ذَيْلًا وَا@دَّرِعْ لَيْلًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Use thou prudence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"precaution,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good judgment, and journey all the night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"drE","text_ar":"درع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He strove,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"laboured, exerted himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability, employed himself vigorously"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"laboriously"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with energy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took extraordinary pains,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, Msb, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and was quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amara","text_ar":"شَمَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amorN","text_ar":"شَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlEibaAdapi","text_ar":"فِى العِبَادَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in religious service"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY sayorihi","text_ar":"فِى سَيْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeying"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajar~ada","text_ar":"تَجَرَّدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ainojarada","text_ar":"اِنْجَرَدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L and TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jrd","text_ar":"جرد"},{"kind":"text","text":".) Also, (K,) inf. n. as above; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amara","text_ar":"شَمَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amorN","text_ar":"شَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"An$mr","text_ar":"انشمر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$m~r","text_ar":"تشمّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He passed along striving,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exerting himself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vigorously:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he passed along with a proud and self-conceited gait;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) [and] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mar~a ya$omuru","text_ar":"مَرَّ يَشْمُرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above, has the latter meaning. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$m~r fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"شمّر فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for, the affair:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$m~r liloA^amori","text_ar":"شمّر لِلْاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$m~r liloA^amori A^a*oyaAlahu","text_ar":"شمّر لِلْاَمْرِ اَذْيَالَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$m~r Eano saAqihi","text_ar":"شمّر عَنْ سَاقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active, and he rose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastened, to do the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$m~rt","text_ar":"شمّرت"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHarobu","text_ar":"الحَرْبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$m~rt Eano saAqihaA","text_ar":"شمّرت عَنْ سَاقِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The war,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"battle, became vehement;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka$afato Eano saAqK","text_ar":"كَشَفَتْ عَنْ سَاقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He contracted"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qal~aSa","text_ar":"قَلَّصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [and so, perhaps, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amara","text_ar":"شَمَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~amoru","text_ar":"الشَّمْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqoliySu Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"تَقْلِيصُ الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~a$omiyru","text_ar":"التَّشْمِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [or the author of the TA may have misunderstood this explanation in the K, and the meaning may be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became contracted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qal~aSa","text_ar":"قَلَّصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is trans. and also (like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSa","text_ar":"قَلَصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":") intrans.: that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$m~r","text_ar":"شمّر"},{"kind":"text","text":"has this latter meaning, whether it have also, or have not, the former, is shown by the statement that] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$am~arati Al$~afapu","text_ar":"شَمَّرَتِ الشَّفَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qalaSat","text_ar":"قَلَصَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lip became contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became contracted upwards"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qlS","text_ar":"قلص"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t$m~r","text_ar":"تشمّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in like manner] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became contracted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqal~aSa","text_ar":"تَقَلَّصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-  Also, (inf. n. as above, As, S,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He launched forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"a ship, or boat;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"go; let"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"take its course;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, IAar, S, A, K;) and in like manner, a hawk; (A;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he discharged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"an arrow: (As, IAar, S, A, Msb:) and hence, (As, S,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sent, sent forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sent away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, M, A, K,) a thing. (M, A.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sam~ara","text_ar":"سَمَّرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$m~r AlA_ibila","text_ar":"شمّر الاـِبِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A$mrhA","text_ar":"اشمرها","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened the camels; made them to hasten;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akoma$ahaA","text_ar":"اَكْمَشَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which seems to be either syn. with, or a mistranscription for,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kam~a$ahaA","text_ar":"كَمَّشَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sam~ara","text_ar":"سَمَّرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEojalahaA","text_ar":"اَعْجَلَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K, TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$am~arotu Aln~axola","text_ar":"شَمَّرْتُ النَّخْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I cut off the fruit of the palm-trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Saramotuhu","text_ar":"صَرَمْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, TA;) or so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amarotuhu","text_ar":"شَمَرْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ibn-'Abbád, O,) [for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~amoru","text_ar":"الشَّمْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiraAmu Aln~axoli","text_ar":"صِرَامُ النَّخْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","K","TA","AA","As","IAar","M"]},{"entry_id":"n22971","headword_ar":"شِمْرٌ","root":"$mr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a man, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Light, agile,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active; acute,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sharp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick, in intellect; clever, knowing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intelligent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zawolN","text_ar":"زَوْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSiyrN","text_ar":"بَصِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (ElMuärrij, O, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqidN","text_ar":"نَاقِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O, K;) thus accord. to the copies of the K [probably from the O]; but in the Tekmileh &c.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAfi*","text_ar":"نَافِذ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which I regard as the right reading, meaning one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who acts with a penetrative energy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who is sharp, vigorous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"effective,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in everything."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$am~ariY~N","text_ar":"شَمَّرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Liberal, bountiful, munificent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generous;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and courageous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]},{"entry_id":"n22972","headword_ar":"شَمَرٌ","root":"$mr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amaArN","text_ar":"شَمَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}